    public abstract class AbstractAmpAutoCompleteTextField<CHOICE>
extends AbstractAutoCompleteTextField<CHOICE>
implements org.apache.wicket.ajax.IAjaxIndicatorAware
    Encapsulates a "google suggest" textbox - auto complete text field for AMP designed to return the selected object (not the string). This class also implements IAjaxIndicatorAware making the control show a LOADING icon whenever an async request is made
    See Also:
    AmpAutocompleteFieldPanel, Serialized Form
